-- Volkswagen to Make Electric Version of Up! in Slovakia, HN Says
-- B y   R a d o s l a v   T o m e k
-- 2012-03-02T08:13:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-02/volkswagen-to-make-electric-version-of-up-in-slovakia-hn-says.html
Volkswagen AG (VOW)  chose its Slovak
factory to produce an electric version of the carmaker’s new Up!
subcompact model, Hospodarske Noviny  reported , citing Albrecht
Reimold, the head of the Slovak unit.  The carmaker also maintains its plan to reach the Slovak
unit’s full annual production capacity of 400,000 cars as early
as this year, the newspaper cited Reimold as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Radoslav Tomek in Bratislava at 
 rtomek@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
